node.text:
I know it’s definitely different for her to get a Father’s Day gift but there is nothing ordinary about our love. I had never gotten the pleasure or the honor to meet my baby’s Dad, Mr. Jesse A. Dupart. I hear so much about him, how loving, brilliant and hard working he was and how she is the spitting image of him. She lights up when she speaks of him. I just wanted a moment to let her know that I am so grateful to him for giving me the greatest gift I’ve ever gotten…HER. 
❤️ @darealbbjudy ❤️ Thank you Pa🙏🏽#sosoblessed #HappyheavenlyFathersDay

node.text: Shout out to the bestie o mine @mariahcarey as we celebrate the 12 year anniversary of this song. Mad love to @cynthiabailey for givin us Fiddy Cynt  @50cent and @janetjackson for goin all out this one halloween transforming into my big bruh-bruh @jermainedupri. #epic #transformations And if you wanna go deep into these stories, get the memoirs by @mariahcarey OUT NOW‼️ I have the audio version and ALL of our personal stories are in it too. LAWD‼️ Brace yourselves. #sosodef #sosoblessed  # sosomariah We ❤️ u JD‼️ @jermainedupri and mad love to my fam @kandi in the pic w Janet. #deadpresidents
